12.short_description: Frontierre is something that is not explored … yet. The last and farthermost limit of knowledge or settlement beyond which lies the vast,

18.description:
Frontierre is something that is not explored … yet. The last and farthermost limit of knowledge or settlement beyond which lies the vast, wild and unknown. Frontierre is the new found land for the first-comers and adventurous. This is what Frontierre is all about- your springboard into new ventures, experiences, friendships and alliances across distances and cultures.

Frontierre is the new found land of social eMarket, connecting travellers and Travel and Tourism organisations and powered by the two forces: social network and eMarket.

With our family and friends scattered all over the world, we have long dreamt of a consolidated web platform that will make it possible to plan the entire travel, including places to stay and visit, in one go. To get to see and meet local people and explore local tourism opportunities. To share the experiences with our old friends and keep connections with the new ones that we meet on our journeys. To get inspired, and importantly, to connect to service providers directly to get better deals surpassing the intermediaries and language barriers.

Equally the T&T industry is seeking to improve and increase direct contact with their customers, as well as direct booking and marketing. To streamline their information and channel it towards their guests, uplift and maintain customer loyalty and satisfaction. Reach out to new audiences. Ultimately- to get closer and more social with travellers.

On Frontierre travellers and T&T organisations and businesses are equals in their social interaction with each other, pursuing the common goal of discovering and providing better, unique travel deals and opportunities. The vision is to have all sorts of T&T organisations onboard – national tourism organisations and consulates, hotels, B&Bs and hostels, restaurants and cafes, museums and clubs, local guides and global travel guide services and databases interacting casually and socially with various travellers.

Frontierre is all about direct information sharing and connectivity in the pursuit of global travelling and tourism.

12.short_description: A social media company, helping Latin American businesses connect with consumers worldwide through a multi-language directory &

18.description:
A social media company, helping Latin American businesses connect with consumers worldwide through a multi-language directory & travelguides.

CityVoz, Latin America's multilanguage directory, was founded in Santiago, Chile in 2011. Entreprenuer Francisco Poblete moved back to Chile and quickly realized after trying to find a place to live that it was almost impossible to find local business information on the web. Most businesses in Chile do not have a website presence and the local directories are only in Spanish. So CityVoz was founded with the intention of helping local business owners promote their services in a multilanguage directory and to allow locals and travelers to find places and share their personal experiences.

18.description:
The story of LTE is one of a group of visionaries who, decided to disrupt the status quo in 2011 by establishing a new company that offer wide variety of products that meet the needs of your business, incentive, event, conference/ meeting and individual/group travel as well as those who travel for pleasure and adventure, or others wishing to engage in something a little more authentic: homestays.

Since they themselves were incessant travelers, their enormous dreams fueled the company’s leaders to steer LTE to deliver expert local knowledge and logistical fulfillment, along with an amazing selection and variety of ideal locations across Peru.

Our clients prefer to travel with us because they know they can rely on us 24 hours a day and we can offer them custom-tailored service and make certain that their trip is absolutely worry free. We promise inspirational proposals with speed, pro-active communication and value.

LTE wants to be recognized for its commitment to the principles of social and environmental responsibility, aiming to create sustainable and inclusive tourism. This commitment to excellence and quality reaches far beyond the confines of its business objectives.

With expertise in not only luxury but culture, wildlife and history as well, LTE reveals your destination with an authenticity beyond the reach of any other DMC company.
